---

## AI Virtual Try-On Application -- Detailed Implementation Plan

### 1. Design System Setup

#### 1.1 Color Palette (Fashion Minimalist with Warm Coral Accent)

The current `/app/src/index.css` has an empty `:root` block. It needs to be populated with CSS custom properties. The current shadcn/ui setup in `/app/tailwind.config.ts` already maps `hsl(var(--...))` tokens to Tailwind classes, so defining the HSL values in `:root` is all that is needed for the entire color system to work.

**File: `/app/src/index.css`** -- Replace the empty `:root` with these HSL values:

```css
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap');

@layer base {
  :root {
    --background: 0 0% 100%;           /* Pure white */
    --foreground: 0 0% 8%;             /* Near black for text */

    --card: 30 20% 99%;                /* Barely warm white for cards */
    --card-foreground: 0 0% 8%;

    --popover: 0 0% 100%;
    --popover-foreground: 0 0% 8%;

    --primary: 8 65% 65%;              /* Warm coral/rose -- the accent */
    --primary-foreground: 0 0% 100%;   /* White text on coral */

    --secondary: 30 15% 96%;           /* Warm light gray */
    --secondary-foreground: 0 0% 15%;

    --muted: 30 10% 95%;               /* Muted warm gray */
    --muted-foreground: 0 0% 45%;

    --accent: 30 15% 94%;              /* Warm off-white accent */
    --accent-foreground: 0 0% 10%;

    --destructive: 0 72% 51%;
    --destructive-foreground: 0 0% 100%;

    --border: 30 10% 91%;              /* Subtle warm gray border */
    --input: 30 10% 91%;
    --ring: 8 65% 65%;                 /* Coral ring to match primary */

    --radius: 0.5rem;

    /* Custom app tokens */
    --fashion-coral: 8 65% 65%;
    --fashion-rose: 350 50% 72%;
    --fashion-gold: 38 60% 62%;
    --fashion-cream: 40 30% 97%;
    --fashion-charcoal: 0 0% 18%;
  }

  * {
    @apply border-border;
  }

  body {
    @apply bg-background text-foreground;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  h1, h2, h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }
}
```

**Key design decisions:**
- Inter for body text (clean, modern, great readability)
- Playfair Display for headings (fashion editorial feel, like ZARA)
- Warm coral (`hsl(8, 65%, 65%)`) as the primary accent -- not purple
- All neutrals have a slight warm undertone (`hue: 30`) to avoid clinical coldness
- Custom `--fashion-*` tokens for specialized use beyond the shadcn system

