### 7. Page-by-Page Design

#### 7.1 Landing Page (`/app/src/pages/Index.tsx`)

**Layout:**
- Full-viewport hero section with a large fashion image background (or split layout)
- Clean navigation header (logo + minimal links)
- Hero: Large serif headline ("Your Perfect Fit, Reimagined"), subtext, and a single prominent CTA button ("Start Try-On")
- Below the fold: "How It Works" -- 3 steps with icons (Upload, Select, Generate)
- Below that: Features section -- 3 cards highlighting AI accuracy, clothing variety, instant results
- Minimal footer

**Components used:**
- `Header` (custom)
- `HeroSection` (custom) -- uses `framer-motion` for fade-in animations
- `HowItWorksSection` (custom) -- uses `Card` from shadcn
- `FeaturesSection` (custom)
- `Button` (shadcn) for CTA
- `Footer` (custom)

**Key styling:**
- Hero image: full-width with overlay gradient, or side-by-side split (image left, text right)
- CTA button: Custom variant using `bg-fashion-coral hover:bg-fashion-coral/90 text-white` with generous padding (`px-10 py-4 text-lg`)
- Generous spacing: `py-24` between sections, `tracking-tight` on headings

#### 7.2 Upload Page (`/app/src/pages/UploadPage.tsx`)

**Layout:**
- Header with step indicator (Step 1 of 3)
- Centered content area with:
  - Large drop zone (dashed border, icon, text)
  - Below the drop zone: guidelines card (tips for best results)
- Once uploaded: drop zone transitions to a photo preview with "Change Photo" and "Continue" buttons

**Components:**
- `PhotoDropZone` -- Core upload interaction
  - Uses native HTML5 drag-and-drop API
  - `<input type="file" accept="image/*">` hidden behind styled trigger
  - Dashed border with `border-2 border-dashed border-muted-foreground/30`
  - Lucide icons: `Upload`, `ImagePlus`, `Camera`
  - Framer Motion: animates on drag hover (scale, border color change)
  - On drop: reads file, creates `URL.createObjectURL()`, stores in Zustand
- `PhotoPreview` -- Shows uploaded image
  - Uses `AspectRatio` (3:4 ratio for portrait)
  - Image with `object-cover`
